WEBVTT

00:17.850 --> 00:20.530
[Emperor of Ye]

00:21.960 --> 00:24.160
Prince Qi, please come with me.

00:42.640 --> 00:44.790
Your Majesty, Xiao Wuyi campaigned
in the Northern Border,

00:44.790 --> 00:46.710
repelled Northern Qin,
and recaptured five cities.

00:46.710 --> 00:47.770
He is a man of merit.

00:48.110 --> 00:49.000
Killing him

00:49.240 --> 00:51.520
would only sadden our friends
and gladden our enemies.

00:51.520 --> 00:53.380
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

00:57.000 --> 00:58.280
Mother was right.

00:59.560 --> 01:00.890
An emperor cannot allow

01:01.560 --> 01:03.490
another power to exist at his side.

01:04.200 --> 01:05.310
It seems tonight

01:06.710 --> 01:08.640
will be another bloodbath.

01:09.710 --> 01:12.120
I am willing to vouch for Young Lord Xiao.

01:13.150 --> 01:14.789
You're just a prince.

01:15.680 --> 01:17.940
What gives you the right to vouch for him?

01:19.280 --> 01:20.680
Wuyi is my best

01:21.150 --> 01:22.200
and only friend.

01:22.480 --> 01:23.610
He will listen to me.

01:24.400 --> 01:25.920
Please give me a chance, Your Majesty.

01:25.920 --> 01:27.640
I will persuade Wuyi
to withdraw his troops.

01:27.640 --> 01:29.350
And please keep Xiao Wuyi

01:29.640 --> 01:32.440
and Prince Jing'an's Mansion safe,
Your Majesty.

01:34.150 --> 01:34.950
Grand Tutor.

01:37.190 --> 01:38.600
You were indeed right.

01:39.640 --> 01:43.640
Prince Qi is the only perfect solution
for tonight.

01:45.060 --> 01:46.640
Just do as you said.

01:49.920 --> 01:52.000
Yes, Your Majesty.

01:56.950 --> 01:57.810
Your Highness,

01:58.479 --> 02:01.640
from now on,
there won't be Yaoyao anymore.

02:03.150 --> 02:06.210
The peace of the world
and the survival of the royal clan

02:08.030 --> 02:10.750
all depend on you alone, Your Highness.

03:40.240 --> 03:44.190
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:44.640 --> 03:47.190
[Episode 4]

03:48.000 --> 03:50.000
All I want is peace across the realm.

03:51.310 --> 03:52.970
Are you willing to grant that?

04:03.710 --> 04:04.400
Your Highness,

04:04.400 --> 04:06.360
rebellions in the capital
have all been quelled.

04:06.360 --> 04:07.120
The troops have assembled.

04:07.120 --> 04:09.050
We can enter the palace at any time.

04:10.280 --> 04:11.610
Wait for news from Wuyi.

04:12.180 --> 04:12.650
Yes.

04:13.520 --> 04:15.580
One hundred thousand Beifu soldiers

04:16.510 --> 04:18.170
are just outside the city now.

04:19.670 --> 04:20.870
I have already said,

04:21.480 --> 04:23.820
as long as you hand over
your military power,

04:23.820 --> 04:25.620
I can restore peace to the world.

04:26.360 --> 04:27.560
I can also promise you

04:27.800 --> 04:31.130
to erect a monument for
the 30,000 soldiers who died in vain.

04:31.630 --> 04:34.270
But if you refuse
to hand over your military power,

04:34.270 --> 04:35.920
I will have to be ruthless.

04:38.190 --> 04:41.250
So what if the Beifu soldiers
are just outside the wall?

04:41.270 --> 04:44.510
You, Young Lord Xiao,
have already fallen into my trap.

04:45.040 --> 04:46.240
They cannot save you.

04:47.310 --> 04:50.360
I'll just say Prince Changsha
killed Young Lord Xiao.

04:51.120 --> 04:52.720
What can your Beifu soldiers

04:53.310 --> 04:54.480
do to me?

04:58.920 --> 05:01.800
His Highness Prince Qi has arrived!

05:09.800 --> 05:11.660
Why aren't Mao and Lejun here yet?

05:12.040 --> 05:13.560
Shouldn't they have left the city
long ago?

05:13.560 --> 05:14.120
My Lady,

05:15.310 --> 05:18.070
did you hear any fighting
in the city when we left?

05:18.310 --> 05:19.190
Fighting?

05:20.160 --> 05:21.800
Why do I feel that when we left the city,

05:21.800 --> 05:23.190
I didn't even see a soul?

05:23.920 --> 05:25.270
Cang'er, did you hear it?

05:25.270 --> 05:26.200
I didn't either.

05:27.000 --> 05:28.600
Then perhaps I misheard.

05:30.300 --> 05:32.960
Could something have happened
to Mao and Lejun?

05:33.630 --> 05:34.760
Let's go back first.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.240
If we go back now,

05:36.240 --> 05:38.390
wouldn't we be walking right into a trap?

05:38.390 --> 05:39.720
Let's wait a bit longer.

05:43.680 --> 05:45.680
No one said a carriage was prepared.

05:47.830 --> 05:49.240
My Lady, Her Highness ordered that

05:49.170 --> 05:51.270
[Shadow Envoy]

05:49.430 --> 05:51.360
you must leave with me immediately.

05:51.360 --> 05:52.420
Here is the letter.

05:53.510 --> 05:54.390
Mother's private seal?

05:54.000 --> 05:55.670
[Go now]

05:57.430 --> 05:58.830
But I have to wait for Mao.

05:58.830 --> 06:01.160
Prince Qi has already entered the palace.
He can't come.

06:01.160 --> 06:02.690
Why did he enter the palace?

06:02.690 --> 06:03.680
There's no time to explain.

06:03.680 --> 06:05.410
My Lady, please leave quickly.

06:15.320 --> 06:16.120
Father?

06:16.510 --> 06:17.310
Yaoyao,

06:18.090 --> 06:20.090
I'm here to take you back to the city.

06:21.360 --> 06:21.870
My Lord,

06:22.630 --> 06:23.920
Her Highness wants My Lady to leave.

06:23.920 --> 06:25.250
Mind your own business!

06:25.740 --> 06:26.800
I won't go with you.

06:27.190 --> 06:28.390
I will not marry Xiao Wuyi.

06:28.390 --> 06:29.800
I'm leaving with Mao.

06:31.000 --> 06:32.330
By His Majesty's order:

06:32.630 --> 06:34.950
I have learned that Prince Changsha has
committed treason and besieged the palace.

06:34.950 --> 06:36.120
Such fratricide

06:36.159 --> 06:37.190
pains me deeply.

06:37.280 --> 06:41.140
[Xuanzheng Hall]

06:37.750 --> 06:39.240
Fortunately, Prince Qi was astute

06:39.240 --> 06:40.340
and reported it.

06:40.680 --> 06:42.270
With Young Lord Xiao
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

06:42.270 --> 06:43.560
he entered the palace
to quell the rebellion.

06:43.560 --> 06:44.820
I am deeply comforted.

06:45.630 --> 06:46.830
His Majesty is awake?

06:47.920 --> 06:49.040
When?

06:49.870 --> 06:51.190
His Majesty has another edict:

06:51.190 --> 06:52.680
I am prone to illness.

06:53.040 --> 06:55.310
Prince Qi, Li Mao, is wise and perceptive,

06:55.310 --> 06:56.640
resembling me greatly.

06:56.720 --> 06:58.710
He is hereby ordered
to enter the Eastern Palace

06:58.710 --> 07:00.030
and serve as Regent.

07:08.070 --> 07:09.270
Where is His Majesty?

07:09.430 --> 07:10.830
Appointing a Regent
is of utmost importance.

07:10.830 --> 07:12.560
How could it be handled so hastily?

07:12.560 --> 07:13.360
Your Majesty.

07:13.640 --> 07:14.540
His Majesty said,

07:14.540 --> 07:16.600
"I understand Mother's intentions,

07:16.700 --> 07:19.870
but worldly affairs
must follow their natural course.

07:20.200 --> 07:22.200
Forcing them will only backfire."

07:22.750 --> 07:23.950
Does His Majesty know

07:24.560 --> 07:25.390
that releasing Xiao Wuyi

07:25.390 --> 07:26.630
is like letting a tiger
return to the mountain?

07:26.630 --> 07:27.750
I didn't hesitate to get my hands dirty

07:27.750 --> 07:29.070
to eliminate Xiao Wuyi.

07:29.070 --> 07:30.570
This wasn't just for His Majesty,

07:30.570 --> 07:32.720
but to permanently remove a threat to Ye.

07:32.720 --> 07:34.180
What is His Majesty doing?

07:34.510 --> 07:36.240
"No egg stays intact
in an overturned nest."

07:36.240 --> 07:39.409
Ye cannot survive without Xiao Wuyi now.

07:42.000 --> 07:44.920
Tonight, Prince Changsha
committed treason and besieged the palace.

07:44.920 --> 07:47.310
Prince Qi and Young Lord Xiao
quelled the rebellion together.

07:47.310 --> 07:50.640
His Highness appreciated Prince Qi's
loyalty and bravery,

07:50.950 --> 07:53.310
and has appointed him as Regent.

07:53.630 --> 07:54.360
Impossible.

07:54.630 --> 07:56.190
The imperial edict has been issued.

07:56.190 --> 07:59.120
His Highness and Princess Pingning
have entered the Eastern Palace.

07:59.120 --> 08:00.180
As for you, Yaoyao,

08:00.430 --> 08:03.720
you must marry into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion tonight.

08:05.830 --> 08:07.830
Prince Qi, receive the edict.

08:10.720 --> 08:14.040
You want to ensure the coexistence
of Xiao Wuyi and the Empress Dowager,

08:14.040 --> 08:17.680
and the coexistence of Beifu soldiers
and the Li family's empire.

08:17.680 --> 08:18.560
So today,

08:19.980 --> 08:21.740
no matter what edict I issue,

08:22.530 --> 08:24.730
are you willing to stand with Xiao Wuyi,

08:25.560 --> 08:27.420
through fortune and misfortune,

08:27.750 --> 08:29.270
and share life and death?

08:35.950 --> 08:37.549
She is still waiting for you.

08:38.630 --> 08:39.240
Come.

08:44.870 --> 08:45.510
Wuyi.

08:46.150 --> 08:47.150
Tonight, are you really going to...

08:47.150 --> 08:48.150
Think carefully.

08:48.790 --> 08:50.390
If you receive this edict...

08:50.440 --> 08:52.510
you will never be able to
leave Jiankang Palace in your life.

08:52.510 --> 08:53.960
No matter who wins today,

08:54.240 --> 08:56.120
the world will be thrown into chaos.

08:56.120 --> 08:56.630
Wuyi.

08:57.360 --> 08:59.030
I have experienced war
since I was a child.

08:59.030 --> 09:00.750
I know what kind of hell it is.

09:12.390 --> 09:13.150
My Lady, go!

09:13.150 --> 09:13.670
Go!

09:17.340 --> 09:17.790
Go!

09:26.550 --> 09:26.960
Cang'er!

09:26.960 --> 09:27.630
Yaoyao.

09:27.990 --> 09:28.800
Father.

09:29.960 --> 09:31.240
Listen to me.

09:33.840 --> 09:34.750
Father?

09:34.910 --> 09:35.790
Run, My Lady!

09:36.320 --> 09:37.150
Run, My Lady!

09:38.320 --> 09:39.120
Cang'er!

09:39.390 --> 09:40.080
Cang'er!

09:40.390 --> 09:40.920
Cang'er!

09:41.750 --> 09:42.280
Cang'er!

09:42.840 --> 09:43.480
Cang'er!

09:45.600 --> 09:46.390
Cang'er!

09:47.910 --> 09:48.750
Cang'er!

09:56.520 --> 09:57.390
Xie Jiayu!

09:58.200 --> 09:59.800
Are you going to listen to me?

10:04.270 --> 10:05.510
Please don't kill her!

10:05.510 --> 10:06.440
I'll go with you!

10:06.950 --> 10:07.920
I'll go with you!

10:16.550 --> 10:18.150
Why did your shoe fall off?

10:18.840 --> 10:20.960
Come, let me put it on for you.

10:21.720 --> 10:23.870
A bride must be beautiful.

10:26.750 --> 10:27.800
I thought you

10:28.590 --> 10:30.720
were a gentleman admired by everyone.

10:31.440 --> 10:33.240
I've never seen you kill anyone.

10:34.290 --> 10:34.930
Why?

10:36.670 --> 10:37.960
Why did you do this?

10:44.790 --> 10:45.960
Don't cry.

10:48.120 --> 10:48.960
Yaoyao,

10:50.630 --> 10:51.890
you should grow up now.

10:53.440 --> 10:56.100
The first thing you learn
when you grow up is that

10:56.360 --> 10:58.090
sometimes, you have no choice.

10:58.960 --> 11:00.080
Mao had no choice.

11:01.150 --> 11:02.480
And so do you.

11:06.130 --> 11:08.270
I thought you loved me the most.

11:09.630 --> 11:12.790
Everyone has a scale in their heart,

11:14.380 --> 11:17.080
weighing what is important
and what is more important.

11:17.080 --> 11:19.440
So you must marry Xiao Wuyi.

11:20.440 --> 11:22.670
Is... Is it for the Xie family?

11:25.820 --> 11:26.620
Take her away.

11:32.240 --> 11:34.510
Father! Tell me the reason!

11:35.080 --> 11:37.020
Why must I marry Xiao Wuyi?

11:37.870 --> 11:38.720
Why?

11:39.080 --> 11:41.840
You will be happier if you don't know.

11:43.120 --> 11:44.200
I want to know.

11:46.150 --> 11:47.000
It's for Mao.

11:48.720 --> 11:52.630
Prince Jing'an's Mansion commands
the Beifu Army of 200,000 soldiers.

11:52.630 --> 11:53.600
They're ambitious

11:53.600 --> 11:55.720
and can change the dynasty at any time.

11:55.720 --> 11:57.520
But why haven't they done it yet?

11:57.550 --> 11:58.960
Because there are noble families

11:58.960 --> 12:00.090
like our Xie family,

12:00.270 --> 12:01.730
supporting His Highness—

12:02.120 --> 12:04.650
or you can say
supporting the Li royal family.

12:05.610 --> 12:08.030
So even if the Xiao family
takes the throne,

12:08.030 --> 12:09.750
they won't be able to sit securely on it.

12:09.750 --> 12:12.670
But you never wanted
to associate with the Xiao family.

12:12.670 --> 12:14.120
If I run away from the wedding now

12:14.120 --> 12:15.520
and break ties with them,

12:15.960 --> 12:17.360
wouldn't that be better?

12:17.600 --> 12:19.660
Maybe we could have done that before,

12:20.550 --> 12:23.750
but now the Regent is Mao.

12:24.550 --> 12:26.630
If Prince Jing'an's Mansion
has rebellious intentions,

12:26.630 --> 12:27.790
Mao, as the Regent,

12:28.150 --> 12:29.680
will have no way to survive.

12:31.840 --> 12:32.670
For Mao,

12:32.670 --> 12:33.910
for the Xie family,

12:35.240 --> 12:37.840
you must be this pawn.

12:40.240 --> 12:41.000
Father,

12:43.550 --> 12:45.350
I don't seem to know you anymore.

12:50.120 --> 12:50.780
Because...

12:52.550 --> 12:54.080
it's time for you to grow up.

13:05.910 --> 13:07.960
All troops, heed my command!

13:20.940 --> 13:22.070
Greetings, Father.

13:23.750 --> 13:25.150
Prince Jing'an, Xiao Ju,

13:25.360 --> 13:27.390
and the Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Wuyi,

13:27.390 --> 13:29.050
receive the imperial decree.

13:32.670 --> 13:34.000
Prince Changsha has committed treason,

13:34.000 --> 13:35.320
and his crime is punishable by death.

13:35.320 --> 13:38.480
The Xiaos received the decree to mobilize
the Beifu Army to suppress the rebellion.

13:38.480 --> 13:39.720
Their loyalty is commendable,

13:39.720 --> 13:41.050
and We are very pleased.

13:41.080 --> 13:43.870
I hereby appoint Xiao Ju
as Grand General of National Defense,

13:43.870 --> 13:46.120
and Young Lord Xiao
as General of National Support.

13:46.120 --> 13:47.920
Young Lord Xiao is ordered to...

13:54.150 --> 13:56.020
To marry the daughter of the Xie family.

13:56.020 --> 13:58.120
The Beifu Army must return immediately

13:58.120 --> 13:58.980
without delay.

14:00.030 --> 14:01.630
Yes, Your Majesty.

14:02.150 --> 14:04.910
Furthermore, Prince Changsha deployed
military equipment without authorization,

14:04.910 --> 14:07.150
causing the innocent deaths
of Beifu soldiers.

14:07.150 --> 14:08.210
I am deeply pained.

14:08.550 --> 14:09.810
Prince Changsha's private properties
shall be confiscated

14:09.810 --> 14:11.600
to console the soldiers' families.

14:11.600 --> 14:14.630
A Monument of Loyalty shall be erected
and recorded in history

14:14.630 --> 14:17.030
to honor the loyalty
of the Beifu soldiers.

14:17.080 --> 14:19.680
Thank you, Your Majesty,
for your great grace.

14:33.410 --> 14:33.970
Wuyi,

14:34.510 --> 14:35.480
you have sought justice

14:35.480 --> 14:37.340
for the soldiers who died in vain.

14:37.440 --> 14:39.240
As for what happened tonight...

14:39.910 --> 14:40.510
I know.

14:41.510 --> 14:42.120
She...

14:42.390 --> 14:43.650
Don't worry about her.

14:45.630 --> 14:46.760
Tell her to wait for me.

14:46.760 --> 14:47.670
I will find a way.

14:47.670 --> 14:48.240
Alright.

14:48.630 --> 14:49.890
I will pass it on to her.

14:52.270 --> 14:54.360
But there's something I want to ask you.

14:54.360 --> 14:56.600
Who brought you back tonight?

14:57.510 --> 14:58.310
It was Master.

15:02.150 --> 15:03.080
The Grand Tutor?

15:03.760 --> 15:04.560
What's wrong?

15:07.720 --> 15:08.250
Nothing.

15:09.590 --> 15:10.510
General Xiao,

15:10.950 --> 15:12.480
Prince Qi, Young Lord Xiao.

15:16.360 --> 15:17.240
Regarding the rebellion tonight,

15:17.240 --> 15:19.550
Young Lord Xiao, thank you
for your bravery and righteousness

15:19.550 --> 15:21.250
in saving the people from suffering

15:21.250 --> 15:23.200
and rescuing the court
from imminent peril.

15:23.200 --> 15:26.360
The Empress Dowager
specially ordered me to thank you

15:26.720 --> 15:28.520
for saving our lives on behalf of

15:28.670 --> 15:31.200
all the officials
and the people of the realm.

15:49.670 --> 15:50.390
Son.

15:51.630 --> 15:55.430
What were you and Prince Qi silently
communicating with each other?

15:56.150 --> 15:57.120
After tonight,

15:59.910 --> 16:02.040
Yizhi won't just be Prince Qi anymore.

16:04.000 --> 16:05.460
He will also be the Regent.

16:06.720 --> 16:07.480
What?

16:08.750 --> 16:09.360
Father,

16:10.200 --> 16:10.870
I'll...

16:11.470 --> 16:12.530
go for a walk alone.

16:25.930 --> 16:29.250
I have brought Jiayu back.

16:34.120 --> 16:36.120
Congratulations, Young Lord Xiao,

16:36.240 --> 16:38.600
for seeking justice
for the soldiers who died in vain.

16:38.600 --> 16:41.400
You played the Empty City Stratagem
beautifully.

16:41.510 --> 16:42.390
I'm impressed.

16:43.440 --> 16:44.900
Grand Tutor, why don't you

16:45.080 --> 16:46.280
just speak your mind?

16:46.720 --> 16:48.600
The Beifu Army
brought back by the Old Prince

16:48.600 --> 16:49.800
is at most 10,000 men.

16:50.550 --> 16:53.610
If they had really fought
the Imperial Guards tonight,

16:53.840 --> 16:55.500
the outcome would be unknown.

16:55.700 --> 16:57.670
Am I right?

16:58.200 --> 16:59.080
Yizhi said

16:59.680 --> 17:02.210
that he was also escorted back
by you tonight.

17:02.400 --> 17:05.400
Grand Tutor, you never planned
to let them go, did you?

17:08.589 --> 17:11.400
Now the royal family is in decline,

17:11.920 --> 17:13.440
His Majesty is prone to illness,

17:13.440 --> 17:15.990
and the Empress Dowager is dictatorial
and incompetent.

17:15.990 --> 17:18.680
Our Southern Ye
is on the verge of collapse.

17:19.480 --> 17:21.410
Since there is no absolute winner,

17:21.920 --> 17:24.119
it's better to have a win-win situation

17:24.270 --> 17:26.000
and make Prince Qi the Regent.

17:26.800 --> 17:27.920
For you

17:28.400 --> 17:29.750
and the realm,

17:30.440 --> 17:31.640
isn't it a good thing?

17:33.400 --> 17:35.130
You cultivated Yizhi for years

17:35.590 --> 17:36.670
just for today?

17:37.480 --> 17:38.720
In Prince Qi,

17:40.920 --> 17:42.110
I saw hope.

17:42.830 --> 17:44.290
What about your daughter?

17:45.270 --> 17:48.510
Everyone in the city says the Grand Tutor
spoils his daughter the most,

17:48.510 --> 17:50.370
but I think you are just too cruel.

17:51.550 --> 17:53.550
You separated Yizhi and your daughter

17:53.550 --> 17:55.350
just to plant a seed of suspicion

17:55.550 --> 17:57.410
between Yizhi and me, didn't you?

17:57.680 --> 17:59.200
What do you mean by that?

18:00.270 --> 18:01.400
You asked

18:01.960 --> 18:04.310
the Empress Dowager
for this marriage yourself,

18:04.310 --> 18:05.030
didn't you?

18:06.110 --> 18:07.550
As for abandoning Jiayu,

18:07.880 --> 18:09.660
that was Prince Qi's own choice.

18:09.660 --> 18:11.090
You can't blame anyone.

18:11.590 --> 18:12.200
Yes,

18:13.510 --> 18:15.070
but I feel sad for them.

18:15.680 --> 18:17.070
I did it for the realm.

18:17.930 --> 18:19.390
I have a clear conscience.

18:20.750 --> 18:21.680
From tonight on,

18:22.240 --> 18:23.520
Yizhi is the Regent,

18:24.240 --> 18:26.370
and Xie Jiayu is my Secondary Consort.

18:27.030 --> 18:30.000
I hope you stop here, Grand Tutor.

18:45.350 --> 18:48.020
But now the Regent is Mao.

18:49.160 --> 18:51.070
If Prince Jing'an's Mansion
has rebellious intentions,

18:51.070 --> 18:52.400
Mao, as the Regent,

18:52.680 --> 18:54.210
will have no way to survive.

18:54.590 --> 18:55.480
For Mao,

18:55.550 --> 18:56.680
for the Xie family,

18:57.370 --> 18:59.680
you must be this pawn.

19:04.270 --> 19:04.920
Cang'er!

19:23.440 --> 19:25.400
Darling, you're not asleep yet?

19:29.720 --> 19:31.050
Tonight in the capital,

19:31.590 --> 19:33.480
the wind is howling
and the rain is pouring.

19:33.480 --> 19:34.350
Lord Xie,

19:35.150 --> 19:36.680
was the road easy to travel?

19:39.830 --> 19:42.240
There is no wind or rain.

19:43.720 --> 19:46.070
It did rain a little just now.

19:47.270 --> 19:48.270
The rain stopped.

19:48.350 --> 19:49.610
The sky has cleared up.

19:53.400 --> 19:54.330
Where is Yaoyao?

19:54.750 --> 19:56.920
Tonight is Yaoyao's wedding night.

19:57.920 --> 20:01.160
Naturally,
she is at Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

20:01.790 --> 20:03.240
But if you miss her,

20:03.680 --> 20:06.540
you can see her again
when she returns in three days.

20:06.590 --> 20:07.070
You killed

20:07.070 --> 20:09.400
the secret guard I sent to protect Yaoyao?

20:14.540 --> 20:17.270
I don't understand
what you are saying, Darling.

20:17.310 --> 20:17.960
Fine.

20:19.000 --> 20:22.000
Then I will say something
you can understand, My Lord.

20:22.880 --> 20:26.110
Your son has become the Regent.

20:27.020 --> 20:30.000
Are you satisfied now, My Lord?

20:38.200 --> 20:39.680
I am thirsty.

20:40.550 --> 20:41.830
I'll go get a cup of tea.

20:45.160 --> 20:46.030
Lord Xie.

20:47.380 --> 20:49.610
That Li Mao,
your illegitimate child with Consort An

20:49.610 --> 20:50.740
of the Late Emperor,

20:51.110 --> 20:53.480
was finally pushed into the position
of Regent by you.

20:53.480 --> 20:54.640
After years of painstaking efforts,

20:54.640 --> 20:56.500
you have finally made it tonight.

20:58.550 --> 20:59.110
My Lord,

21:00.720 --> 21:01.790
are you satisfied?

21:18.240 --> 21:22.570
Are you looking at the Grand Tutor's Mansion
or the Prince Jing'an's Mansion?

21:24.180 --> 21:25.110
Tonight,

21:26.110 --> 21:28.170
you shouldn't have made this choice.

21:29.000 --> 21:29.930
I didn't choose.

21:32.200 --> 21:33.860
It was just a stalling tactic.

21:36.510 --> 21:38.190
Wuyi and I will find a way.

21:40.440 --> 21:41.160
Brother.

21:42.230 --> 21:44.030
I think one day,

21:45.390 --> 21:47.320
you will regret today's decision.

22:11.830 --> 22:12.690
Your Highness.

22:16.960 --> 22:18.220
Let her sleep in peace.

22:18.590 --> 22:19.790
I won't go in tonight.

22:20.160 --> 22:20.840
Wait.

22:28.110 --> 22:28.970
Your Highness,

22:29.510 --> 22:30.910
it's your wedding night.

22:31.430 --> 22:32.560
Where are you going?

22:34.070 --> 22:34.790
Xie Jiayu,

22:36.190 --> 22:37.250
you want me to stay?

22:44.070 --> 22:44.750
Husband,

22:45.440 --> 22:46.770
it's our wedding night,

22:46.790 --> 22:49.050
and we haven't drunk the nuptial cup yet.

22:52.200 --> 22:54.000
Don't worry. It's not poisoned.

23:46.720 --> 23:47.480
Xie Jiayu,

23:48.030 --> 23:49.830
can you come up with some new tricks?

23:49.830 --> 23:51.290
Do you think I'm Qing Long?

23:53.720 --> 23:55.240
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

23:55.510 --> 23:56.720
You treat me like this.
Do you believe I'll...

23:56.720 --> 23:57.480
What?

23:57.960 --> 24:00.420
That your father
will come and take you back?

24:09.880 --> 24:11.270
We've been busy all night

24:11.270 --> 24:12.330
and haven't eaten.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.400
Stop struggling,

24:17.590 --> 24:19.120
or your hands will get hurt.

24:19.200 --> 24:20.310
When you go crying to Yizhi,

24:20.310 --> 24:21.480
don't blame it on me.

24:22.440 --> 24:23.070
Yizhi?

24:24.270 --> 24:25.110
You know Mao?

24:34.310 --> 24:35.790
This is Mao's personal jade pendant.

24:35.790 --> 24:36.790
Why do you have it?

24:36.920 --> 24:38.120
What did you do to Mao?

24:39.640 --> 24:40.750
I abducted him.

24:41.200 --> 24:42.200
I snatched it.

24:51.000 --> 24:51.840
Hurry up and eat.

24:51.840 --> 24:52.700
Why did you kick me?

24:52.700 --> 24:55.160
Aren't you hungry
after fighting all night?

24:56.510 --> 24:58.070
I don't know what you like to eat,

24:58.070 --> 25:00.160
so I just grabbed some from the kitchen.

25:00.160 --> 25:00.840
Have a taste.

25:00.840 --> 25:03.900
The lamb shoulder from our small kitchen
is quite good.

25:11.240 --> 25:12.040
What's wrong?

25:13.400 --> 25:14.240
Nothing.

25:14.600 --> 25:16.130
I just suddenly remembered

25:17.470 --> 25:19.360
that Cang'er used to love lamb.

25:29.790 --> 25:32.000
Wait. I thought about it carefully,

25:32.510 --> 25:34.640
and it seems to have gone too smoothly.

25:35.590 --> 25:36.750
You searched the whole city,

25:36.750 --> 25:37.960
but no one found me.

25:38.680 --> 25:40.880
Then something happened in the palace.

25:40.880 --> 25:42.440
Then you went to the palace
to suppress the rebellion,

25:42.440 --> 25:43.900
and Mao became the Regent.

25:45.370 --> 25:47.100
There must be something wrong.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.130
Keep analyzing.

25:51.370 --> 25:54.160
Father said
Prince Changsha besieged the palace,

25:54.160 --> 25:56.640
Prince Qi and Young Lord Xiao entered
the palace together to suppress the rebellion,

25:56.640 --> 25:58.900
and His Majesty appointed Mao as Regent.

25:59.030 --> 26:01.230
But Mao clearly wanted to leave with me.

26:01.270 --> 26:03.870
And the map
of the Prince Jing'an's Mansion...

26:05.980 --> 26:07.310
That was a military map,

26:07.350 --> 26:09.280
obviously drawn by a military man.

26:09.920 --> 26:11.110
When Mao gave it to me,

26:11.110 --> 26:12.640
I felt something was wrong.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.350
This map...

26:16.510 --> 26:17.550
You drew this map?

26:20.590 --> 26:22.750
Not bad. You're not too stupid.

26:23.720 --> 26:25.480
You helped Mao and me escape?

26:28.880 --> 26:29.590
No, no.

26:29.880 --> 26:31.550
It's also possible
that you pretended to help Mao,

26:31.550 --> 26:33.070
but in reality, you kidnapped him
and took him to the palace,

26:33.070 --> 26:34.440
forcing him to become the Regent.

26:34.440 --> 26:35.070
You even...

26:35.070 --> 26:36.720
Stop. Cut it out.

26:37.310 --> 26:39.240
I think you should stop analyzing.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.480
It's not impossible.

26:43.350 --> 26:44.880
Mao is my best friend.

26:45.390 --> 26:46.520
Why would I force him

26:46.550 --> 26:48.410
to do things he doesn't want to do?

26:49.070 --> 26:50.530
You are Mao's good friend,

26:50.590 --> 26:54.050
yet you asked the Empress Dowager
to have me marry you in court?

26:56.240 --> 26:57.480
If I had known you two were...

26:57.480 --> 26:58.340
I would have...

27:00.590 --> 27:01.190
Forget it.

27:04.160 --> 27:05.960
"Pine and cypress stand firm in frost.

27:05.960 --> 27:07.830
Wind and rain turn into dragon's roar.

27:07.830 --> 27:09.070
So lofty ambitions

27:09.310 --> 27:10.710
reach the highest peak."

27:10.750 --> 27:12.150
Have you heard this poem?

27:12.920 --> 27:13.680
Mao wrote it.

27:14.110 --> 27:15.770
Do you know who he wrote it for?

27:16.750 --> 27:19.010
You're not saying it was for you, are you?

27:21.510 --> 27:23.310
I knew him when we were nobodies,

27:23.510 --> 27:24.970
much earlier than you did.

27:26.750 --> 27:28.200
You are sinister,

27:28.200 --> 27:29.200
murderous,

27:29.200 --> 27:30.220
cold-blooded, and lustful.

27:30.220 --> 27:32.200
Mao must have been deceived
by your appearance.

27:32.200 --> 27:33.130
That's why he...

27:34.920 --> 27:35.960
Sinister?

27:38.270 --> 27:39.680
Murderous?

27:45.680 --> 27:47.210
Cold-blooded and lustful?

27:50.510 --> 27:52.000
If he weren't my friend,

27:53.310 --> 27:56.240
you wouldn't have the chance
to speak to me like this.

28:03.790 --> 28:04.640
I didn't expect Li Mao

28:04.640 --> 28:05.840
to become the Regent.

28:06.400 --> 28:07.800
It was a stopgap measure.

28:08.440 --> 28:09.720
The situation is unstable.

28:09.720 --> 28:10.400
He can't leave,

28:10.400 --> 28:11.530
and neither can you.

28:12.000 --> 28:13.060
From this night on,

28:13.440 --> 28:14.350
you, Xie Jiayu,

28:14.680 --> 28:17.920
shall be the Secondary Consort
of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

28:17.920 --> 28:18.920
For Li Mao's sake,

28:19.220 --> 28:20.950
you'd better behave yourself,

28:20.960 --> 28:22.290
playing your role well.

28:23.310 --> 28:24.570
When the time is right,

28:24.640 --> 28:26.300
I will arrange for you to meet.

28:26.790 --> 28:28.160
Whether you're going to stay or leave,

28:28.160 --> 28:30.090
we can talk about it after you meet.

28:30.720 --> 28:31.400
Xiao Wuyi.

28:33.590 --> 28:35.320
Are you really Li Mao's friend?

28:39.590 --> 28:41.050
If you want me to believe you,

28:41.050 --> 28:42.200
take me out of the city tonight.

28:42.200 --> 28:42.550
No.

28:43.720 --> 28:45.640
I am Xiao Wuyi, a murderous man.

28:46.200 --> 28:48.000
So you'd better behave yourself

28:48.160 --> 28:49.030
and stay put.

29:03.130 --> 29:03.820
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

29:03.820 --> 29:04.750
Do you want some?

29:10.830 --> 29:13.490
Your Highness,
is there something on your mind?

29:17.200 --> 29:20.260
The Grand Tutor's appearance tonight
was unexpected.

29:21.550 --> 29:23.590
How did you find out
that the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

29:23.590 --> 29:25.640
was the one who designed
the repeating crossbow?

29:25.640 --> 29:26.720
After the incident at Jiuzhang Plain,

29:26.720 --> 29:28.200
you ordered us
to return to the capital immediately

29:28.200 --> 29:30.720
to secretly investigate the Vice Minister
in charge of weapons manufacturing.

29:30.720 --> 29:31.920
We found the blueprint
of the repeating crossbow

29:31.920 --> 29:33.580
in Vice Minister Wei's study.

29:33.720 --> 29:36.750
That blueprint had the mark
of the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

29:36.750 --> 29:38.480
So we followed the clues.

29:39.110 --> 29:39.640
Yes.

29:39.880 --> 29:40.920
This Young Master of Miraculous Craft

29:40.920 --> 29:42.400
is not hard to find in Jiankang.

29:42.400 --> 29:44.270
He's always been selling goods
at Xiyue Restaurant.

29:44.270 --> 29:46.000
Although he doesn't have
a fixed stall or shop,

29:46.000 --> 29:47.960
he is very close
to the owner of Xiyue Restaurant.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.790
So, under the guise of doing business,

29:49.790 --> 29:51.790
we asked the owner to invite him out.

29:51.830 --> 29:53.890
And that was how you caught Xie Jiayu?

29:54.030 --> 29:55.720
This three-foot,
four-arrow repeating crossbow

29:55.720 --> 29:57.320
was custom-made for a buyer.

29:57.350 --> 29:58.350
His surname is...

29:58.490 --> 29:59.000
Xiao.

29:59.200 --> 30:00.730
And his given name is Sheng.

30:02.070 --> 30:05.070
But we found out that Xie Jiayu
didn't know anything about it.

30:05.070 --> 30:07.270
Your Highness, is there something wrong?

30:07.270 --> 30:08.270
Nothing is wrong.

30:10.000 --> 30:11.400
It's just that all of this

30:12.310 --> 30:13.640
went a bit too smoothly.

30:13.960 --> 30:15.830
The Empress Dowager has lived
deep in the palace for a long time.

30:15.830 --> 30:17.480
How could she know that there was a

30:17.480 --> 30:19.720
Young Master of Miraculous Craft
in Jiankang,

30:19.720 --> 30:21.110
and even know what she could

30:21.110 --> 30:22.310
and couldn't design?

30:23.590 --> 30:25.520
There must be some connection here

30:25.750 --> 30:27.270
that we don't know about.

30:33.240 --> 30:34.900
I hope it's not what I suspect.

30:37.030 --> 30:38.590
Then I will continue to investigate
Xiyue Restaurant.

30:38.590 --> 30:39.390
Investigate?

30:39.790 --> 30:40.590
It's too slow.

30:47.720 --> 30:48.270
My Lady.

30:48.680 --> 30:49.680
Actually, I think

30:50.240 --> 30:51.970
Young Lord Xiao and his 2 guards

30:52.550 --> 30:54.400
are not as scary as rumors say.

30:55.720 --> 30:57.650
Don't believe everything he says.

30:57.720 --> 31:01.240
Did you forget what happened
at Xiyue Restaurant and the ferry?

31:01.240 --> 31:02.750
So you mean...

31:02.920 --> 31:05.380
Who knows if this guy
is being honest with us?

31:06.400 --> 31:07.880
We can't let our guard down.

31:07.880 --> 31:08.590
Stay alert.

31:08.750 --> 31:09.240
Yes.

31:36.720 --> 31:39.430
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

31:39.880 --> 31:40.830
I'm so sleepy.

31:50.070 --> 31:50.990
Mother-in-law, Father-in-law,

31:50.990 --> 31:52.520
I'm here to pay my respects.

31:59.400 --> 32:00.830
Mother-in-law, Father-in-law?

32:00.830 --> 32:01.680
Little beast,

32:02.070 --> 32:03.200
where are you going?

32:03.400 --> 32:03.960
Darling,

32:04.270 --> 32:05.800
bring me my Qinglong Sword!

32:05.990 --> 32:08.270
I must chop this thing into pieces today!

32:09.000 --> 32:09.680
My Lady.

32:10.550 --> 32:13.150
Prince Jing'an's Mansion
is indeed like hell.

32:13.510 --> 32:14.270
Hold it down.

32:14.590 --> 32:16.230
Should I chop its legs or its waist?

32:16.230 --> 32:17.360
Chop the head first!

32:23.070 --> 32:24.070
Xie, you're here?

32:26.920 --> 32:27.920
Do you like

32:27.920 --> 32:29.680
duck heads, wings, or legs?

32:40.480 --> 32:41.740
Make yourself at home.

32:42.070 --> 32:43.600
Thank you, Mother-in-law.

32:45.440 --> 32:47.310
As their newly wedded daughter-in-law,

32:47.310 --> 32:48.920
I wasn't asked to pay my respects

32:48.920 --> 32:49.980
or learn any rules?

32:57.030 --> 32:58.070
I have military affairs to attend to.

32:58.070 --> 32:58.870
I'll go first.

32:59.880 --> 33:01.210
What military affairs?

33:01.480 --> 33:03.030
You must be itching

33:03.030 --> 33:04.200
to play cards, huh?

33:04.350 --> 33:05.000
Darling.

33:05.830 --> 33:07.690
I've been at the border for years,

33:08.000 --> 33:09.350
leading troops in battles every day,

33:09.350 --> 33:10.880
setting an example myself.

33:11.000 --> 33:13.400
I've finally returned to the capital. I...

33:14.440 --> 33:16.920
I'll go back to the Northern Border
in a few days.

33:16.920 --> 33:18.380
As a respectable general,

33:19.070 --> 33:21.000
is it really too much
to play a few rounds of cards,

33:21.000 --> 33:21.510
Xie?

33:22.310 --> 33:23.310
Just a few rounds.

33:25.840 --> 33:26.700
I'm telling you,

33:26.700 --> 33:28.000
if you lose everything,

33:28.000 --> 33:29.240
don't even think about coming back home.

33:29.240 --> 33:29.920
I won't. I won't.

33:29.920 --> 33:30.750
I won't lose.

33:32.150 --> 33:32.790
Xie,

33:32.860 --> 33:35.010
drink less soup. It's too salty.

33:38.450 --> 33:40.940
The Prince used to be a stableboy,

33:41.320 --> 33:43.120
and I am a butcher's daughter.

33:43.200 --> 33:45.530
So there are no strict rules
in our family.

33:46.700 --> 33:47.700
That brat,

33:48.030 --> 33:49.690
why did he marry so many wives?

33:51.070 --> 33:52.240
We can't blame him.

33:52.640 --> 33:54.550
Since you are here,

33:54.760 --> 33:56.620
just stay here with peace of mind.

33:57.400 --> 33:58.860
Alright, Mother-in-law.

33:58.900 --> 34:00.250
Drink the soup.

34:06.070 --> 34:07.960
The Xiao family is so strange.

34:08.630 --> 34:10.800
The Old Prince
doesn't look like a general at all.

34:10.800 --> 34:12.280
The Princess is also strange.

34:12.280 --> 34:13.400
As a Buddhist,

34:13.550 --> 34:14.590
how can she eat meat at every meal

34:14.590 --> 34:15.850
and not avoid killing?

34:22.230 --> 34:23.090
Your Highness.

34:23.480 --> 34:24.630
The Northern Border is cold.

34:24.630 --> 34:25.800
I had people skin

34:25.800 --> 34:27.280
20 white foxes

34:27.280 --> 34:28.590
to make 2 cloaks.

34:29.000 --> 34:31.480
I'll have them sent
to Prince Jing'an's Mansion after court

34:31.480 --> 34:33.800
as my farewell gift.

34:33.920 --> 34:35.719
You are about to return
to the Northern Border.

34:35.719 --> 34:38.360
We haven't got a chance
to catch up with the Old Prince yet.

34:38.360 --> 34:41.190
Why don't we find a time
to hold a banquet?

34:41.400 --> 34:42.730
Who said I'm going back?

34:43.989 --> 34:45.409
Are you all hoping

34:45.440 --> 34:47.400
I'll return to the Northern Border soon,

34:47.400 --> 34:49.440
so you can live a life of pleasure
in Jiankang,

34:49.440 --> 34:50.770
getting lost in comfort

34:51.199 --> 34:53.400
and never thinking of returning north?

34:53.400 --> 34:54.130
In that case,

34:54.840 --> 34:56.320
let me tell you now—

34:56.880 --> 34:59.610
I'm not returning to the Northern Border
for now.

35:01.510 --> 35:04.320
The Empress Dowager is here!

35:15.320 --> 35:19.190
Greetings, Empress Dowager.
Greetings, Your Highness.

35:19.400 --> 35:20.190
You may rise.

35:26.760 --> 35:28.220
Young Lord Xiao was right.

35:28.590 --> 35:29.760
In the battle at Jiuzhang Plain,

35:29.760 --> 35:31.440
Northern Qin lost despite outnumbering us.

35:31.440 --> 35:33.000
The Emperor of Northern Qin was furious,

35:33.000 --> 35:35.440
and the Eagle King, commander
of the Black Eagle Army, was demoted.

35:35.440 --> 35:37.850
The Emperor of Northern Qin
sent an envoy for peace talks,

35:37.850 --> 35:38.690
and I agreed.

35:39.510 --> 35:41.400
At that time, we will need Young Lord Xiao

35:41.400 --> 35:43.510
to preside over the peace talks
in Jiankang.

35:43.510 --> 35:45.800
Hasn't Young Lord Xiao been focusing
on the northern expedition?

35:45.800 --> 35:46.790
I'll do my expedition,

35:46.790 --> 35:47.990
and you do your talks.

35:48.960 --> 35:49.920
These two things
can proceed at the same time.

35:49.920 --> 35:51.030
And we can continue the expedition
after the talks.

35:51.030 --> 35:52.360
What's wrong with that?

35:52.670 --> 35:54.250
But what about
the Beifu soldiers outside the city?

35:54.250 --> 35:57.250
The Northern Qin peace talks
are fraught with danger.

35:58.110 --> 36:00.360
In my opinion, during the peace talks,

36:00.510 --> 36:02.870
the Beifu Army
still needs to garrison Jiankang

36:02.870 --> 36:05.400
to ensure the safety of His Majesty
and the Empress Dowager.

36:05.400 --> 36:06.840
What do you think, Your Majesty?

36:06.840 --> 36:07.840
Young Lord Xiao,

36:08.630 --> 36:12.290
are you going to leave the army
at the Northern Border unattended?

36:14.550 --> 36:16.400
Your Majesty, you don't need to worry.

36:16.400 --> 36:17.760
After the Double Ninth Festival sacrifice,

36:17.760 --> 36:20.360
my father will immediately return to
the Northern Border to command the army.

36:20.360 --> 36:21.550
During the peace talks,

36:21.550 --> 36:24.000
we will never let the border
be taken advantage of by others.

36:24.000 --> 36:26.480
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

36:26.920 --> 36:29.550
Prince Jing'an and Young Lord Xiao
have thought things through.

36:29.550 --> 36:30.590
That's good.

36:31.440 --> 36:33.400
I also plan to pray
for the sacrificed Beifu soldiers

36:33.400 --> 36:35.060
at the Double Ninth Ceremony.

36:35.800 --> 36:37.070
The Beifu soldiers
stationed outside the city

36:37.070 --> 36:38.510
should also participate.

36:38.510 --> 36:40.440
What do you think, Young Lord Xiao?

36:40.550 --> 36:43.010
Yes, Your Majesty.
Thank you, Your Majesty.

36:44.440 --> 36:45.670
If there's nothing else,

36:45.670 --> 36:46.730
I'll take my leave.

36:52.800 --> 36:53.600
Your Majesty,

36:53.710 --> 36:55.370
I will see Young Lord Xiao out.

37:06.070 --> 37:06.760
Wonderful.

37:07.090 --> 37:07.890
With you in Jiankang,

37:07.890 --> 37:08.690
I'm relieved.

37:10.710 --> 37:11.360
How is she?

37:13.230 --> 37:15.510
She probably wants
to poison me to death right now,

37:15.510 --> 37:16.800
but for your sake,

37:17.000 --> 37:18.260
she hasn't done it yet.

37:18.470 --> 37:19.510
If you dare bully her,

37:19.510 --> 37:20.570
I won't let you off.

37:22.290 --> 37:23.220
I wouldn't dare.

37:25.230 --> 37:26.160
Young Lord Xiao.

37:27.070 --> 37:29.070
Lady Xie is the beloved daughter
of my master.

37:29.070 --> 37:32.000
And this marriage was granted
by the Empress Dowager.

37:32.000 --> 37:33.190
Whether you like it or not,

37:33.190 --> 37:34.800
you should treat her well.

37:35.070 --> 37:35.710
Yes.

37:36.280 --> 37:38.070
Lady Xie is well-educated

37:38.090 --> 37:39.090
and gentle.

37:39.670 --> 37:40.400
She is proficient

37:40.400 --> 37:41.440
in all kinds of women's skills,

37:41.440 --> 37:43.400
as well as poetry and history.

37:43.550 --> 37:45.190
I will treat her well.

37:45.870 --> 37:48.030
And I thank the Empress Dowager
for granting the marriage.

37:48.030 --> 37:49.760
I heard the pear blossom candy
at Chengyi Hall in the south of the city

37:49.760 --> 37:51.000
is especially delicious.

37:51.000 --> 37:52.670
The ladies in Jiankang are crazy about it.

37:52.670 --> 37:55.800
Whenever they are in a bad mood,
they will buy some to eat.

37:55.840 --> 37:57.400
If you're in a bad mood,

37:57.760 --> 37:59.090
you might as well try it.

37:59.840 --> 38:00.970
I don't like sweets,

38:01.480 --> 38:02.510
I'm not a lady,

38:03.000 --> 38:04.930
and I'm in a pretty good mood today.

38:04.960 --> 38:06.360
I didn't ask you to eat it.

38:07.000 --> 38:07.800
Got it.

38:08.600 --> 38:09.330
So annoying.

38:14.360 --> 38:16.640
You have served His Majesty and
the Empress Dowager for many years.

38:16.640 --> 38:18.230
You are the head
of the eunuchs in the palace,

38:18.230 --> 38:20.190
so naturally you are a sensible person.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.550
The peace in Southern Ye today

38:21.550 --> 38:23.320
does not depend on good weather,

38:23.320 --> 38:25.110
nor on the kindness of the people,

38:25.110 --> 38:28.040
but on me and the Beifu soldiers
guarding the border.

38:28.400 --> 38:30.400
The Empress Dowager and I are now at peace

38:30.400 --> 38:32.600
because we have Prince Qi as the Regent.

38:33.100 --> 38:35.230
I hope you can remind the Empress Dowager

38:35.230 --> 38:38.230
not to follow the disastrous path
of Prince Changsha.

38:39.440 --> 38:41.480
If Prince Qi doesn't even have freedom,

38:41.480 --> 38:44.280
wouldn't it be a joke
to the envoys of Northern Qin?

38:46.920 --> 38:48.780
That's what Young Lord Xiao said.

38:50.400 --> 38:51.200
Your Majesty,

38:51.670 --> 38:53.330
what Young Lord Xiao meant was

38:53.800 --> 38:56.460
that the court and the harem
should value peace.

38:56.670 --> 38:58.800
He kept the Beifu soldiers in Jiankang

38:58.920 --> 39:01.440
to protect you and His Majesty.

39:01.800 --> 39:02.760
He and my brother...

39:02.760 --> 39:05.000
When have I ever blamed Young Lord Xiao?

39:07.500 --> 39:08.540
Well,

39:09.290 --> 39:10.690
who taught you the rules?

39:11.770 --> 39:13.590
My sister and I
have been orphans since childhood

39:13.590 --> 39:14.590
and had only each other.

39:14.590 --> 39:16.920
She has neglected her etiquette studies.

39:17.000 --> 39:19.060
Please don't be angry, Your Majesty.

39:20.510 --> 39:21.170
Never mind.

39:23.280 --> 39:24.960
From now on, you will live with me

39:24.960 --> 39:26.280
in Ziji Palace,

39:26.710 --> 39:28.360
learning the rules for a few years,

39:28.360 --> 39:29.920
so you can find a good match.

39:31.110 --> 39:31.590
Your Majesty...

39:31.590 --> 39:33.280
Since she has neglected her etiquette,

39:33.280 --> 39:35.010
she should be properly taught.

39:38.800 --> 39:39.600
In the future,

39:41.190 --> 39:43.190
she will become the Grand Princess,

39:43.840 --> 39:45.480
the face of our Ye.

39:46.410 --> 39:48.740
If she is so ignorant of proper etiquette,

39:48.960 --> 39:52.690
wouldn't the world laugh at our Ye
for having no sense of propriety?

39:52.780 --> 39:55.260
Not to mention she is already of age.

39:56.030 --> 39:56.880
You two

39:57.030 --> 39:59.740
shouldn't live
in the same palace anymore anyway.

39:59.740 --> 40:00.530
He Tian,

40:01.800 --> 40:04.840
take Princess Pingning
to the Eastern Palace to pack her things

40:04.840 --> 40:06.900
and move to Ziji Palace immediately.

40:07.150 --> 40:08.230
From today on,

40:08.800 --> 40:09.480
I

40:10.570 --> 40:13.370
will personally teach her
the rules of the palace.

40:13.400 --> 40:14.150
Yes.

40:16.150 --> 40:16.710
Your—

40:18.400 --> 40:19.550
Yes, Your Majesty.

40:20.600 --> 40:21.960
To be taught by you

40:22.110 --> 40:23.320
is my blessing.

40:29.040 --> 40:29.730
Lejun.

40:40.330 --> 40:41.990
What are you still doing here?

40:42.480 --> 40:43.810
You'll be offering sacrifices

40:43.810 --> 40:45.790
on behalf of His Majesty
at the Double Ninth Ceremony.

40:45.790 --> 40:48.650
Have you learned all the etiquette
and procedures?

41:06.840 --> 41:07.670
Fight,

41:08.920 --> 41:09.960
scramble,

41:11.480 --> 41:12.320
and struggle.

41:13.400 --> 41:16.260
Now that you've stepped into
the storm of Jiankang,

41:17.480 --> 41:20.410
who here isn't making moves
with their lives at stake

41:22.190 --> 41:25.050
while pretending every day
that they want nothing?

41:26.110 --> 41:27.320
Life is so boring.

41:32.880 --> 41:35.150
Little fish, tell me.

41:36.710 --> 41:39.150
Will they turn on their own kin first,

41:41.360 --> 41:43.960
or will they start fighting
among themselves,

41:45.670 --> 41:46.630
or will

41:47.400 --> 41:50.080
those who love each other
end up killing one another?

41:50.080 --> 41:51.510
Have you ever thought that this scheme

41:51.510 --> 41:52.970
would ruin Yaoyao's life?

41:55.710 --> 41:56.670
Xie Jiayu

41:57.880 --> 41:59.610
is nothing but a stranger to me.

42:01.510 --> 42:02.320
Wuyi,

42:03.110 --> 42:05.710
when you saved me
among the refugees back then,

42:06.030 --> 42:07.230
we were also strangers.
